{"tid":1862240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]美國航空暫停往返香港航班","createTime":"2020-02-04T13:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T15:37:43.000Z","uid":34119,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd637542ccd666d020abd13034190a9ca3878c69","tid":1862240,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506652-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506652-20200204.htm&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3T632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=8c81a87b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506652-20200204.htm&h=b54b1f90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506652-20200204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n本港出現首宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎死亡病例，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全美最大的航空公司美國航空宣布，即日暫停由洛杉磯和達拉斯往返香港的所有航班，直至今個月20日</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，美國政府對中國實施航班與旅客入境限制，未有包括港人在內。美國航空在上周五已經宣布暫停往返中國的航班，直到下月27日。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國外相藍轁文發表聲明，呼籲在華英國公民盡可能離開中國，未來數周或出現航班限制，會令公民難以離開。"},{"pid":"9f01fd42cc68bdca8bdc223b2a0aaca5d5639110","tid":1862240,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3da86fe77ab427aff9ab777513d4070747f893","tid":1862240,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"548e0ec0c3e37e9d33da8789301ecb16f8d9bc4d","tid":1862240,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"老燒段片岩岩講完，老美就出手"},{"pid":"d301c1c6bfe3dfba9fe3b5d034e2ed949fff4fa6","tid":1862240,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"無啦... 香港人真係要暴動了<br />\n2 月尾 ... 應該香港人連逃出機會都無埋 ... <b